author: brane
msg: Reworked the Win32 build again. No more environment variables, no more
special settings in MSVC. The Berkeley DB includes and libs must now
live under db3-win32 in the root of the Subversion source tree.
Also fixed some test driver .dsps so that all tests can now be built
* *.dsp: Look for DB3 includes in .../db3-win32/include; look for
import libs in .../db3-win32/lib. Fix library paths in several test
